    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that \"win-win\" framing seems a bit optimistic though. most of the business owners i talk to are worried about immediate bankruptcy or seeing their shops close down because they can't afford the tech upgrades. is there any real evidence that these \"new green jobs\" actually replace the manufacturing jobs being lost in these specific communities, or is that just a theoretical possibility?",
